headline: UP, Norfolk Southern Push Back on Class I Challenges to Merger Filing
summary: The railroads say competitors’ objections are “baseless” and improperly argue the merits rather than the completeness of the filing.

headline: 3 Large-Cap Stocks We’re Skeptical Of
summary: Large-cap stocks usually command their industries because they have the scale to drive market trends. The flip side though is that their sheer size can limit growth as expanding further becomes an increasingly challenging task.
